column2: "Oh! I completely forgot to register this quest!"
"Hmmm.... hmmmmmm! Um... write this, and fill out that..."

"S-sorry, <%me>,
but do you know what time it is?"
"Sorry about the delay. Let's get going!"
"It looks like we're out really early today."
"There's still nobody out here yet. A quest so early in the day is a nice change of pace."
